/// Error — Non-resumable exceptions.
///
/// Subclass of Exception for errors that cannot be resumed.
/// Maps to Erlang's `error` class in try/catch.
///
/// ## Examples
/// ```beamtalk
/// [1 / 0] on: Error do: [:e | e message]
/// ```
///
/// @see Exception (for resumable exceptions)
/// @see Result (for expected success/failure without exceptions)
Exception subclass: Error
